"AAP2073N2XXF10" and "Made In Taiwan" is silkscreened :on the main board in the FCC photos. "AAP2073N1XXF10" and "Made In Taiwan" is silkscreened :on the Power / HomePlug board.
The device uses an ''[[Intellon]]'' chipset for HomePlug AV.
The manual states the default SSID is '''wlan_ap'''... with a possible :OUI of 00:04:ED (also shown on the FCC sample label).
